{"tid":1373053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得今日班和理非好抵讚","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T14:54:00.000Z","uid":93080,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d582515f1dbf6e4518a4c2a82703f8c31658b6","tid":1373053,"uid":93080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:27:38.000Z","msg":"平時嘅話，佢哋應該死都唔肯做犯法嘅嘢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>但係</strong></span></span><br />\n今日竟然個個都出晒去元朗買老婆餅<br />\n今日係28萬8千人出咗嚟<br />\n真係好感動<br />\n呢個垃9圾政府終於都逼到班和理非都要企出嚟<br />\n多謝晒今日出嚟行嘅和理非巴打同絲打<br />\n更加要多謝一班企喺和理非前面幫我哋擋棍擋槍嘅勇武派巴絲打<br />\n香港人，加油"},{"pid":"153579bc8f80c96c708146f1cb442f350cc164bf","tid":1373053,"uid":91154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2f28990ead0a861eeb08db349578197254d6ca","tid":1373053,"uid":93080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"41747671277611cd448d08527e4e70f832b55996","tid":1373053,"uid":93080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:29:55.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"45f377387ac6e2dc0768778ae114e489af53cae4","tid":1373053,"uid":93080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"3458ecc04637dabfd7f61d8f8ec1331fcd444916","tid":1373053,"uid":93080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"cbda1ac654ef3a6fde8ee9f30a7a578f9a90ccfb","tid":1373053,"uid":93080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"0d5a6e84e1a9d3cf419244375caa9d0896698ccc","tid":1373053,"uid":93080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:33:10.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"51e62372747d33f4a307716c446f46bb9e2cbbe6","tid":1373053,"uid":93080,"